      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUGOLD NZ (10) is a three-year-old colt by leading sire Captaintreacherous on debut for top trainer Luke McCarthy. Draws on the back row but has been showing some ability in his trials at Menangle and has the right credentials to play a major role. STOLEN ONE (9) made an encouraging debut when he clocked in fourth last start at Melton, beaten 7.6 metres. Draws for a trail and has scope for improvement with that run under the belt. WARRAWEES SHOUT (11) may need some luck from his second row draw but has been coming from wide barriers and producing some decent results including a placing three back at Menangle. THE KID BILLY (1) gets the ace draw and could be close to a win having come from tougher barriers for second in his last two outings.",
